00:21:47,973 --> 00:21:49,099
<i>It's Malone...</i>

343
00:21:51,643 --> 00:21:53,145
<i>And it's Utah with the lead.</i>

344
00:21:53,729 --> 00:21:56,189
<i>Only moments ago, they trailed by nine.</i>

