674
00:43:15,426 --> 00:43:18,095
I'd been signing one-year contracts
up to that.

675
00:43:18,178 --> 00:43:20,264
Would Phil have done it? Yes.

676
00:43:20,347 --> 00:43:22,766
Now, Pip,
you would've had to do some convincing,

677
00:43:22,850 --> 00:43:24,476
