678
00:43:24,560 --> 00:43:27,271
if Dennis was gonna be there,
if MJ was gonna be there,

679
00:43:27,813 --> 00:43:31,150
to win our seventh,
Pip is not gonna miss out on that.

680
00:43:33,402 --> 00:43:35,195
You know, '91-'92, I was...

681
00:43:36,238 --> 00:43:39,825
I was young, full of energy, hungry.

682
00:43:39,908 --> 00:43:44,204
In '98, when you're winning
six out of eight,

