698
00:44:37,132 --> 00:44:38,132
Time to go.

699
00:44:46,308 --> 00:44:49,853
I remember there was this
team meeting with Phil...

700
00:44:51,021 --> 00:44:53,899
and it was like, "This is it."

701
00:44:56,151 --> 00:44:59,196
My wife had gotten her master's
in social work

702
00:44:59,279 --> 00:45:03,117
