713
00:45:50,622 --> 00:45:52,791
Phil had this knack,

714
00:45:52,875 --> 00:45:55,753
no matter how big you are
or how big you think you are,

715
00:45:55,836 --> 00:46:00,174
to always draw you in
to be a part of the process.

716
00:46:01,550 --> 00:46:05,179
I'm not a poet.
I just spoke what I felt at the time.

717
00:46:06,930 --> 00:46:08,390
We're always gonna be bonded.

718
00:46:10,517 --> 00:46:13,187
You say thanks for the past,
enjoy the moment.

719
00:46:13,270 --> 00:46:15,272
Let's make sure we end it right.

720
00:46:17,232 --> 00:46:19,735
We saw him as this bully sometimes.

721
00:46:20,444 --> 00:46:24,156
